headline: Northern Trust’s Amy Szostak Elected an ACTEC Fellow
summary: CHICAGO, April 14, 2025--Northern Trust announced today that Amy Szostak, Director of Family Education and Governance, has been elected a Fiduciary Counsel Fellow of the American College of Trust & Estate Counsel (ACTEC). With Szostak’s appointment, Northern Trust now has 16 ACTEC Fellows.

headline: M&T Bank Corporation (MTB) Q1 Earnings and Revenues Lag Estimates
summary: M&T Bank (MTB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -0.88% and 1.59%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
